sql:
SELECT
id,
category,
prop_type,
Prop_kind,
rental_price,
prop_name,
prop_address,
cea_reg,
concat(lease_duration_no, ' ', lease_duration_unit) AS lease_duration,
land,
tenure,
no_bedrooms,
no_bathrooms,
concat(rental_price, ' ', rental_price_type) AS rental,
`date`,
built_up,
built_up_unit,
land_unit
FROM transactions
ORDER BY `date` DESC, id DESC
